1
00:00:01,000 --> 00:00:03,500
Welcome back to the cutting room.

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:06,250
Today we are looking at the rough cut.

3
00:00:07,000 --> 00:00:11,800
ANNA: I always start with the interview
and build the scene around it.

4
00:00:12,300 --> 00:00:14,000
That gives you a spine.

5
00:00:15,000 --> 00:00:17,500
Then the B-roll goes on top.

6
00:00:18,000 --> 00:00:20,750
Music comes last, never first.

7
00:00:21.100 --> 00:00:23.900
Unless the scene is cut to playback.

8
00:00:24,500 --> 00:00:26,000
Which happens more than you think.

9
00:00:27,000 --> 00:00:29,300
Keep your trims non-destructive.

10
00:00:30,000 --> 00:00:32,000
And always label your reels.
